\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Jan 03, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104fok1665703135432.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/fok1665703135432.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/fok1665703135432.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"fok1665703135432\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"fok1665703135432__unifmes_406329\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Get the text of a Uniface error message.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"fok1665703135432__topic_d122354e1_d122355e1_d122356e1\">\n<div class=\"p\">\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104fok1665703135432_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"fok1665703135432__codeblock_j4m_tc2_bwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">int unifmes (unsigned char*Buffer);</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"fok1665703135432__topic_d86647e1_d86648e1_d86649e1_d86650e1_d86651e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d637799e61\">Parameters</h2>\n<dl class=\"dl parml\" id=\"fok1665703135432__parml_npr_vc2_bwb\">\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">Buffer</var></dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">The message (Output)</dd>\n</dl>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"fok1665703135432__topic_d86652e1_d86653e1_d86654e1_d86655e1_d86656e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d637799e80\">Return Values</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"fok1665703135432__p_d122369e1_d122370e1_d122371e1\">The number of bytes returned (not including the zero terminator)</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"fok1665703135432__topic_d86657e1_d86658e1_d86659e1_d86660e1_d86661e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d637799e89\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"fok1665703135432__d5947e20\">Library:  <span class=\"ph filepath\">yrtl</span>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"fok1665703135432__topic_d86662e1_d86663e1_d86664e1_d86665e1_d86666e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d637799e102\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"fok1665703135432__p_d122381e1_d122382e1_d122383e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">unifmes</code> copies the text of the\n            Uniface start-up error message, which would normally be displayed on standard output or\n            the transcript window, to the specified buffer. This function can be called from a 3GL\n            call-in application when the call to <code class=\"ph codeph\">unifbeg</code> has failed, so it can\n            display the error message. <var class=\"keyword varname\">buffer</var> should be large enough to hold a\n            typical Uniface start-up error message (200 bytes is a safe size).</p>\n<p class=\"p\">The following call-in program starts the Uniface environment with\n               <code class=\"ph codeph\">unifbeg</code>, deliberately asking for a non-existing application shell to\n            cause it to fail, then uses <code class=\"ph codeph\">unifmes</code> to print the exact error\n            message.</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104fok1665703135432_html_1\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"fok1665703135432__codeblock_m3c_yc2_bwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">#include &lt;h3gl.h&gt;\n#include &lt;stdio.h&gt;\n\nvoid main (void)\n{\nchar buf[200];\n\nusetparm(0, \"a_nonexisting_startup_shell.aps\", \"\");\nunifbeg(0);\nunifmes(buf);\nprintf(msg, \"unifbeg() failed, error %d (%s)\\n\", ret, buf);\n}</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/umj1665702596245.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>unifbeg</a><p>Start an application, or initialize the Uniface environment, so forms can be executed.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527600\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527600\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "unifmes Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 03, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Get the text of a Uniface error message. Explain this code int unifmes (unsigned char*Buffer); Copy Parameters Buffer The message (Output) Return Values The number of bytes returned (not including the zero terminator) Use Library: yrtl Description unifmes copies the text of the Uniface start-up error message, which would normally be displayed on standard output or the transcript window, to the specified buffer. This function can be called from a 3GL call-in application when the call to unifbeg has failed, so it can display the error message. buffer should be large enough to hold a typical Uniface start-up error message (200 bytes is a safe size). The following call-in program starts the Uniface environment with unifbeg , deliberately asking for a non-existing application shell to cause it to fail, then uses unifmes to print the exact error message. Explain this code #include <h3gl.h> #include <stdio.h> void main (void) { char buf[200]; usetparm(0, \"a_nonexisting_startup_shell.aps\", \"\"); unifbeg(0); unifmes(buf); printf(msg, \"unifbeg() failed, error %d (%s)\\n\", ret, buf); } Copy Related Links unifbeg Start an application, or initialize the Uniface environment, so forms can be executed. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}